OL,3,CWhy unions are unsatisfied with
OL,4,Cgovernment's latest teacher pay rise
OL,5,Cproposal
OL,7,FThere is very little chance, on a
OL,8,Fsettlement of that magnitude, that the
OL,9,Fchronic shortage of teachers and
OL,10,Fteaching assistance will be remedied.
OL,12,FUnion leaders are already muttering
OL,13,Fabout probable industrial action.
OL,14,FSorry parents.
OL,16,FThe second cause of teachers' concern
OL,17,Fis that any settlement will have to be
OL,18,Ffunded by making cuts to school
OL,19,Fbudgets.
