OL,3,CWhy unions are unsatisfied with
OL,4,Cgovernment's latest teacher pay rise
OL,5,Cproposal
OL,7,FThere will be no additional money for
OL,8,Fsalary increases.
OL,10,FSo where does Bridget Phillipson, the
OL,11,FEducation Secretary, think there is
OL,12,Ffat in schools that can be eliminated?
OL,14,FWell last night she met union leaders
OL,15,Fas a courtesy, to forewarn them about
OL,16,Fher submission to the pay review body.
OL,18,FShe told them she did not want or
OL,19,Fexpect them to find the money by
OL,20,Feliminating core education provision.
